{
  "page": "King of the Dornish",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>King of the Dornish</b> was one of the titles held by King <a href=\"/index.php/Yorick_V_Yronwood\" title=\"Yorick V Yronwood\">Yorick V Yronwood</a>, the last independent <a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">Yronwood</a> king, who resisted the unification of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> under <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria%27s_War\" title=\"Nymeria&#39;s War\">Nymeria's War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The title boasts of authority over the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a> people, likely in the face of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> invasion.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_the_Dornish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_Dorne\" title=\"High King of Dorne\">High King of Dorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_Stone_Way\" title=\"Warden of the Stone Way\">Warden of the Stone Way</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_the_Wells\" title=\"Knight of the Wells\">Knight of the Wells</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Redmarch\" title=\"King of Redmarch\">King of Redmarch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Greenbelt\" title=\"King of the Greenbelt\">King of the Greenbelt</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=King_of_the_Dornish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ten Thousand Ships.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405035024\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 100/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 363/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 113/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 591/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.474      1 -total\n 75.59%    4.138      1 Template:Ref\n 47.03%    2.574      1 Template:Ref/core\n 22.98%    1.258      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21355-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405035024 and revision id 208611\n -->\n",
